        <h4 class="pixel-font uppercase">1. General</h4>
        <p class="text-large">These terms apply to all orders placed through the NoGood shop at nogood.studio. By placing an order you agree to these terms. NoGood is operated as a sole trader based in Amsterdam, the Netherlands.</p>

        <div class="spacer line"></div>

        <h4 class="pixel-font uppercase">2. Products</h4>
        <p class="text-large">All physical products are produced in limited runs. Images are as accurate as possible but slight colour variation may occur due to screen calibration and print processes. Digital products are delivered as-is and are non-refundable once downloaded.</p>

        <div class="spacer line"></div>

        <h4 class="pixel-font uppercase">3. Pricing & Payment</h4>
        <p class="text-large">All prices are listed in euros and include Dutch VAT where applicable. Payment is processed securely via Mollie (credit card, iDEAL) or via Bitcoin and Lightning Network through BTCPay Server. NoGood does not store or handle payment credentials.</p>

        <div class="spacer line"></div>

        <h4 class="pixel-font uppercase">4. Shipping</h4>
        <p class="text-large">Orders are shipped once a week from the studio in Amsterdam using MyParcel. A track & trace code will be sent by email after dispatch. Delivery times vary by destination and are outside of NoGood's control once the package has left the studio. Import duties and local taxes for orders outside the EU are the responsibility of the buyer.</p>

        <div class="spacer line"></div>

        <h4 class="pixel-font uppercase">5. Returns & Damages</h4>
        <p class="text-large">Because products are produced in limited runs, returns are not accepted. If your order arrives damaged, contact <a href="mailto:{{ settings.metadata.site_email }}">{{ settings.metadata.site_email }}</a> within 7 days of delivery with a photo of the damage and it will be made right.</p>

        <div class="spacer line"></div>

